{"title":"心灵短笛（三首）","authors":["陈忠干"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":12,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"心灵短笛（三首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈忠干"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"交替歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬天与春色的交替，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给春天蕴育着蓓蕾萌芽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春季与盛夏的交替，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为夏季布满了绿叶红花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏日与金秋的交替，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把累累的秋实到处结下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大自然的交替是一首颂歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱给我，唱给你，也唱给他！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"代价"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂个名字算什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戴顶乌纱算什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尚余多少工作日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倒需认真争夺它。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活如逆水行舟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时间却顺流而下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史在转折，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"征帆已高挂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心血呵，要多呕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗水呵，需多洒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多为“四化”做贡献，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命才能如火花……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勿忘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国已给，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"独生子女们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蔚蓝色的童年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲啊别忘了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引导孩子们回首，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看自己头上顶过的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——灰暗冬天……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告诉他们："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了得到明天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就应记住昨天！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}